<th class="px-4 py-3 text-left text-xs font-semibold text-gray-700 uppercase tracking-wider">Weaviate Cloud</th>

<th class="px-4 py-3 text-left text-xs font-semibold text-gray-700 uppercase tracking-wider">Qdrant Cloud</th>

<th class="px-4 py-3 text-left text-xs font-semibold text-gray-700 uppercase tracking-wider">Milvus (self-hosted)</th>

